# Snippet to add to your HTTPS VirtualHost for voiceai.tittu.in (e.g. after Certbot).
# This proxies LiveKit WebSocket over HTTPS so you don't need TLS on port 7880.
#
# 1. Enable WebSocket proxy module:
#    sudo a2enmod proxy_wstunnel
#
# 2. In your <VirtualHost *:443> for voiceai.tittu.in, add these lines BEFORE the closing </VirtualHost>:
#
#    # LiveKit WebSocket: proxy /rtc to local LiveKit (plain ws on 7880)
#    ProxyPreserveHost On
#    ProxyPass /rtc ws://127.0.0.1:7880/rtc
#    ProxyPassReverse /rtc ws://127.0.0.1:7880/rtc
#
# 3. In .env set (no port — browser uses 443):
#    LIVEKIT_URL=wss://voiceai.tittu.in
#
# 4. Restart: sudo systemctl restart voiceai-token voiceai-agent && sudo systemctl reload apache2
